    {
      "text": "det å representere flest mulig geografiske områder, ulike aldersgrupper eller lignende",
      "translation": "the state of representing as many geographical areas, different age groups, or the like as possible",
      "examples": [
        {
          "no": "oppfylle kravet om representativitet for kjønn, alder og geografi",
          "en": "meet the requirement of representativeness in terms of gender, age, and geography"
